FUCKING UGLY SHOE EXCITING?

01:22.650 --> 01:24.352
- THE SAME WAY WE MADE
THOSE FUCKING UGLY RAINCOATS

01:24.385 --> 01:25.353
EXCITING LAST MAY.

01:25.386 --> 01:27.121
- MODELS.

