- [chuckles]

04:30.338 --> 04:33.574
- I'M MORE OF
A CAREER DYKE MYSELF.

04:33.607 --> 04:35.509
- I USED TO SAY
THE SAME THING.

04:35.543 --> 04:37.711
THAT WAS UNTIL
WE HAD OUR SON.

04:37.745 --> 04:40.514
- HMM.
- I'M MELANIE MARCUS.

04:40.548 --> 04:42.783
- YEAH, I KNOW.
THE ROLE MODEL.

04:42.816 --> 04:45.919
- I'M MARIANNE MACDONALD.
DEFINITELY NOT A ROLE MODEL.

04:45.953 --> 04:48.055
- WELL, GOOD FOR YOU.

04:48.088 --> 04:50.458
- THOUGH, I SUPPOSE

04:50.491 --> 04:54.862
YOU COULD SAY I AM "PC."

04:54.895 --> 05:00.534
THAT IS, IF PC STANDS FOR
"PERFORMS CUNNILINGUS".

05:00.568 --> 05:03.471
- [laughs]
OH, GOD, YOU'RE WICKED.

05:03.504 --> 05:05.873
- THANK YOU.

05:05.906 --> 05:10.944
