05:39.607 --> 05:40.974
- YOU CAN'T GO.
- WHY NOT?

05:41.008 --> 05:42.843
- YOU'RE IN A RELATIONSHIP.

05:42.876 --> 05:44.478
OR HAVE YOU FORGOTTEN?

05:44.512 --> 05:46.747
- NO MORE FUN FOR YOU.

05:46.780 --> 05:48.849
- OH, DAVID SAID
I COULD GO.

05:48.882 --> 05:50.484
AS LONG AS I BEHAVE MYSELF.

05:50.518 --> 05:52.586
- [scoffs] WELL,
THEN WHAT'S THE POINT OF GOING?

05:52.620 --> 05:54.422
- JUST MEANS MORE MEN
FOR ME AND EM.

05:54.455 --> 05:56.457
RIGHT, EM?

05:56.490 --> 05:57.458
- HUH?

05:57.491 --> 05:59.059
OH, YEAH, YEAH.

05:59.092 --> 06:01.595
- WHAT'S THE MATTER WITH YOU?

06:01.629 --> 06:03.997
- HE'S GOT RAZOR BURN
ON HIS BALLS.

06:04.031 --> 06:04.998
- I'M FINE.

06:05.032 --> 06:06.500
I'M FINE.

06:06.534 --> 06:09.503
- WELL, THEN GET YOUR ASS
ON THE DANCE FLOOR.

06:09.537 --> 06:11.505
