TO P-TOWN.

06:38.131 --> 06:40.634
AND I WANT TO GO.

06:40.668 --> 06:42.002
ALL THOSE MEN,

06:42.035 --> 06:44.738
ALL THOSE DRUGS.

06:44.772 --> 06:47.007
SORRY.

06:47.040 --> 06:50.177
AND THAT'S NOT THE WORST
OF IT.

06:50.210 --> 06:53.514
