THE WATCH

06:53.547 --> 06:55.082
MY GRANDFATHER GAVE ME
ON HIS DEATHBED...

06:55.115 --> 06:58.151
[clears throat]
TO BUY A TICKET FOR

06:58.185 --> 07:00.854
BARBRA'S
ABSOLUTELY FINAL FAREWELL,

07:00.888 --> 07:03.190
I-SWEAR-TO-GOD-THIS-IS-IT
CONCERT.

07:03.223 --> 07:04.592
I MEAN,

07:04.625 --> 07:06.460
I CAN BARELY SURVIVE
ON MY WEEK'S SALARY,

07:06.494 --> 07:08.929
AND I'M GOING TO HELP FILL
MRS. BROLIN'S COFFER?

07:08.962 --> 07:11.164
SICK.

07:11.198 --> 07:12.633
I'M SICK.

07:12.666 --> 07:13.867
- BUT THERE'S A CURE.

07:13.901 --> 07:15.836
THAT'S WHY YOU CAME TO
"SEE THE LIGHT."

07:15.869 --> 07:17.237
BELIEVE ME,
I KNOW HOW YOU FEEL.

07:17.270 --> 07:20.440
I'VE BEEN THERE.

07:21.742 --> 07:23.477
LOOK AT THIS.

07:23.511 --> 07:24.845
WHAT DO YOU SEE?

07:24.878 --> 07:26.179
- A PICTURE OF A DRAG QUEEN.

07:26.213 --> 07:28.549
OR YOUR MOTHER.

07:28.582 --> 07:30.117
- THAT WAS ME.

07:30.150 --> 07:32.686
- NO!
COME ON.

07:32.720 --> 07:33.987
BUT YOU'RE SO...

07:34.021 --> 07:35.923
- STRAIGHT?
THANK YOU.

07:35.956 --> 07:37.958
I KEEP THIS PHOTO
AS A REMINDER

07:37.991 --> 07:39.560
OF MY FORMER LIFE.

07:39.593 --> 07:41.862
BUT EVEN THEN,
I KNEW UNDER ALL THOSE WIGS

07:41.895 --> 07:44.097
AND THOSE FABULOUS GOWNS,

07:44.131 --> 07:47.701
THERE WAS A CONSERVATIVE
REPUBLICAN COMPUTER ANALYST

07:47.735 --> 07:50.671
DYING TO BE FREE.

07:50.704 --> 07:52.540
THAT'S WHAT
"SEE THE LIGHT" DID FOR ME.

07:52.573 --> 07:54.241
AND IT CAN DO THE SAME
FOR YOU,

07:54.274 --> 07:56.644
IF YOU'RE SERIOUS.
- I AM.

07:56.677 --> 07:58.912
I AM SERIOUS,
I SWEAR TO GOD.

07:58.946 --> 08:01.549
- GOOD.
BUT DON'T FOOL YOURSELF.

08:01.582 --> 08:02.716
IT WON'T BE EASY.

08:02.750 --> 08:03.784
AT SOME POINT
YOU MAY EVEN HAVE TO

08:03.817 --> 08:05.018
EXTRICATE YOURSELF FROM

08:05.052 --> 08:07.521
CERTAIN CORRUPT INFLUENCES.

08:07.555 --> 08:09.122
- YOU MEAN MY FRIENDS?

08:09.156 --> 08:10.624
- ARE THEY REALLY
YOUR FRIENDS

08:10.658 --> 08:12.259
IF THEY LEAD YOU
INTO TEMPTATION?

08:12.292 --> 08:14.762
- WELL, THEY NEVER DO IT
DELIBERATELY.

08:14.795 --> 08:17.898
- EMMETT,
IF YOU SEE THE LIGHT,

08:17.931 --> 08:20.568
YOU MUSTN'T ALLOW
ANYTHING OR ANYONE

08:20.601 --> 08:24.538
TO DIVERT YOU
FROM THE PATH.

08:26.740 --> 08:29.309
- THANK YOU, MATT,
FOR YOUR SUPPORT.

08:29.342 --> 08:31.078
- HEY,
THAT'S WHY I'M HERE,

08:31.111 --> 08:35.248
TO MAKE SURE YOU DON'T SLIP.

08:43.624 --> 08:46.059
- BRIAN.

08:46.093 --> 08:48.028
- YOU CEO OF THE COMPANY
YET?

08:48.061 --> 08:49.963
- [chuckles]
GIVE ME A WEEK OR TWO.

08:49.997 --> 08:52.065
SO, MR. RYDER TOLD ME
YOU'RE REALLY GOING TO

08:52.099 --> 08:54.301
USE MY IDEAS
FOR THE SHOE ADS.

08:54.334 --> 08:57.070
- I'LL STEAL ANYTHING GOOD
AND PUT MY NAME ON IT.

08:57.104 --> 08:58.572
- THAT'S GREAT.

08:58.606 --> 09:00.774
ALTHOUGH BOB AND BRAD
AREN'T TOO HAPPY ABOUT IT.

09:00.808 --> 09:02.676
- WELL, PEOPLE WITH NO TALENT
USUALLY AREN'T

09:02.710 --> 09:06.213
WHEN SOMEONE WITH REAL TALENT
COMES ALONG.

09:06.246 --> 09:09.182
- YEAH, I HEAR YOU'RE PRETTY
TALENTED YOURSELF.

09:09.216 --> 09:11.652
IN FACT,
YOU HAVE A REPUTATION.

09:11.685 --> 09:13.053
- I DO?

09:13.086 --> 09:15.756
- FOR BEING THE BEST
ACCOUNT EXEC IN THE COMPANY.

09:15.789 --> 09:19.693
- YEAH. THAT TOO.

09:19.727 --> 09:23.063
- AND THAT'S WHY I ASKED
IF I COULD WORK WITH YOU.

09:23.096 --> 09:24.798
- I THOUGHT RYDER ASSIGNED YOU.

09:24.832 --> 09:26.934
- YEAH. I, UH...

09:26.967 --> 09:28.902
LIED.

09:31.705 --> 09:35.776
- COME HERE FOR A SECOND.
I WANT TO SHOW YOU SOMETHING.

09:35.809 --> 09:38.812
THIS IS A NEW CAMPAIGN
WE'RE STARTING FOR LIBERTY AIR.

09:38.846 --> 09:40.814
I WANT YOU ON THE TEAM.

09:40.848 --> 09:46.153
- OH, MY GOD.
THAT'S--THAT'S FANTASTIC.

09:46.186 --> 09:47.320
WOW.

09:47.354 --> 09:49.623
HOW CAN I EVER THANK YOU?

09:53.193 --> 09:55.963
- BY DOING A GOOD JOB.

09:55.996 --> 09:59.366
- YOU CAN COUNT ON IT.

10:06.674 --> 10:08.608
[door closes]

10:10.744 --> 10:13.246
I JUST WANT YOU TO KNOW
THAT YOU CAN...

10:13.280 --> 10:15.949
YOU CAN COUNT ON ME
FOR ANYTHING.

10:15.983 --> 10:18.251
DAY OR NIGHT.

10:18.285 --> 10:21.188
- WELL, YOU REALLY ARE GOING
FOR THE GOLD WATCH.

10:21.221 --> 10:24.191
- I MEAN IT.

10:28.696 --> 10:32.733
BECAUSE I THINK
YOU'RE REALLY, REALLY AMAZING.

10:38.038 --> 10:41.742
- WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

10:41.775 --> 10:43.076
- SHIT.

10:43.110 --> 10:44.845
I'M SORRY, UM...

10:44.878 --> 10:47.414
I DIDN'T MEAN TO--

10:47.447 --> 10:50.951
LOOK, I-I DON'T KNOW
WHAT I WAS THINKING.

10:52.820 --> 10:55.322
- YEAH, WELL,
WHATEVER IT WAS,

10:55.355 --> 10:59.960
YOU THOUGHT WRONG
BECAUSE...

10:59.993 --> 11:02.195
I'M THE ONE...
[lock clicks]

