DOING IT IN YOUR OFFICE

12:30.283 --> 12:32.953
MAY BE A LITTLE TOO HIGH-RISK
EVEN FOR YOU.

12:32.986 --> 12:35.522
- BUT HE ASKED FOR IT,
HE CAME ON TO ME.

12:35.555 --> 12:37.457
