OPPORTUNITY

12:37.490 --> 12:39.159
AND A GREAT FUCK.

12:39.192 --> 12:42.996
HE HAS NO COMPLAINTS.

12:43.030 --> 12:44.865
- WELL, IT WAS OUR PLEASURE,
FRANNY.

12:44.898 --> 12:46.967
YEAH, WE HAD FUN TOO.

12:47.000 --> 12:49.336
SO, I GUESS
IT'S ANY DAY NOW.

12:49.369 --> 12:50.537
